Sorry to dissollusion you but he is being extradited to England.  We dont fry our criminals around here.  The problem is we havn't enough room to put them in jail either.<br>
<br>
The standard punishment for a paedophille is to put them on the sex offenders list.  This meens every 3 months a social worker comes out to see them and ask if their urges are under control.  As he is unlikely to live in Great Britain he wont even get this.<br>
<br>
However our government considers this punishment extremely severe because offenders stay registered for life instead of just 25 years and out in 10.<br>
